{
  "title": "Fire Charred Canadian Mediterranean Hominy Tagine",
  "description": "A smoky solo-dinner fusion featuring fire-charred white corn and Mediterranean aromatics slow-cooked in a traditional clay vessel.",
  "cuisine": "Canadian-Mediterranean Fusion",
